<lb n="2" break="no"/>mi sōmavāradaṁdu śrī rājaguru kalyāṇaśaktidēvaru tammatamaṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>diru <unclear>dhruvē</unclear>svaradēvara śrīpa<unclear>rva</unclear>take kaḷipuvalli <unclear>pa</unclear>ṁḍyana <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ye kā
